# This file keeps the data/ directory tracked by Git.
# Large dataset files (.npy, .csv) and trained artifacts (.pkl) are excluded via .gitignore
# and must be generated locally.
#
# To regenerate:
#   python src/preprocessing.py   # creates X_train.npy, y_train.npy, scaler.pkl, etc.
#   python src/model_training.py  # creates models/best_model.pkl
